OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777442692
OL,3,CMan arrested after several fires
OL,4,Cstarted overnight
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Fafter several fires were started in
OL,8,FBristol overnight.
OL,10,FAvon and Somerset Police were alerted
OL,11,Fto bin fires in Totterdown at around
OL,12,F3:15am on Monday 27 April. There were
OL,13,Falso several other fires spread across
OL,14,Fareas in the city centre including
OL,15,FTotterdown, Broadmead, Nelson Street,
OL,16,FCorn Street, Welsh Back.
OL,18,FOfficers worked with Bristol City
OL,19,FCouncil's CCTV team to identify the
OL,20,Fpotential suspect.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
