OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777442692
OL,3,CMan arrested after several fires
OL,4,Cstarted overnight
OL,6,FChief Inspector Keith Smith said:
OL,7,F"Officers worked tirelessly overnight
OL,8,Fwith firefighters and council CCTV
OL,9,Fstaff in response to these fires and
OL,10,Fthis led to a man being arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of arson. He was transported
OL,12,Finto custody, where he remains.
OL,14,F"These fires will have a financial
OL,15,Fimpact, including to one business
OL,16,Fwhich sustained some exterior building
OL,17,Fdamage.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
