PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777442692
OL,3,CMan arrested after several fires
OL,4,Cstarted overnight
OL,6,F"Fortunately, we do not believe anyone
OL,7,Fwas injured. Deliberately starting a
OL,8,Ffire is incredibly dangerous and
OL,9,Fanother time could have led to far
OL,10,Fmore serious consequences."
OL,12,FPeople who witnessed the fires being
OL,13,Fstarted, or anyone with information or
OL,14,Ffootage that may assist the forces
OL,15,Fenquiries, is being asked to contact
OL,16,Fthem online or on 101 quoting
OL,17,Freference number 5226114268.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]
